Any ideas???

If this happens again, you can try deleting (or renaming) this file in your
workspace:

workspace/.metadata/.plugins/org.eclipse.core.resources/.snap

This should allow you to restart the crashed workspace.
I have not seen this problem reproduced, and there isn't enough detail here to investigate further. If this happens again in 3.2 or later, please reopen.
